<div class="content-block-restricted" data-anijs="" >
    <div class="sf-Long-text" ><h2 style="text-align:center;">We empower everyday Australians</h2></div>
</div><div class="row">
    <div id="MainContentPlaceholder_C052_Col00" class="sf_colsIn col-md-6">    <div class="image-block image-block--link scroll-reveal" data-anijs="if: , on: , do:  animated, before:scrollReveal, after:">
            <a href="/sponsor-a-child">
                <div class="frame">
                    <img src="https://www.worldvision.com.au/images/default-source/about-us-wva/what-we-do/empower-everyday-australians.jpg?sfvrsn=667d963c_2" alt="Eleni Kallianiotis, a child sponsor, looking at the camera"/>
                </div>
            </a>
                <div class="caption caption--none" >
            <p></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div id="MainContentPlaceholder_C052_Col01" class="sf_colsIn col-md-6">
<div class="content-block-restricted" data-anijs="" >
    <div class="sf-Long-text" ><p>Eleni Kallianiotis started sponsoring a child with World Vision when she finished high school. "I really wanted to do something good &ndash; and I wanted to sort of pay it forward," she explains.</p><p>As a mother of two small children, she appreciates that it also brings something very special to her family.&nbsp;</p></div>
</div>
<div class="content-block-restricted" data-anijs="" >
    <div class="sf-Long-text" ><h5>&ldquo;I&rsquo;m able to share this experience with [my family], especially my son who&rsquo;s four now,&rdquo; Eleni says. &ldquo;It&rsquo;s teaching him kindness and giving, and having someone on the other side of the world that he can write to.&rdquo;</h5></div>
</div><div class="StyledButton-widget text-left " data-alignment="left">
        <a href="/sponsor-a-child" class="btn btn-md btn-primary " >
            <span>Sponsor now</span>
        </a>
</div>

